params.description: The key identifying the display data. This is intended to be used as a label for the display data when viewed in a dax monitoring system.

params.name: data.namespace
params.description: The namespace for the key. This is usually a class name or programming language namespace (i.e. python module) which defines the display data. This allows a dax monitoring system to specially handle the data and perform custom rendering.
